from Purong Hotel.

177
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,360
My name is Xu Miyu.

178
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,300
Or maybe

179
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,800
I can make an appointment for later today

180
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,240
