your most embarrassing moment, huh?

234
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,790
Tell me about it.

235
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,720
Just drop me off
at the intersection ahead.

236
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,440
It's fine. I'll drop you off downstairs.

237
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,240
