be leading our project team.

571
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:44,910
She just won't
have to go it alone anymore.

572
00:25:44,910 --> 00:25:46,690
If anything unexpected comes up,

573
00:25:46,690 --> 00:25:48,970
I'll be there to help her

574
00:25:48,990 --> 00:25:49,990
manage the risks.

575
00:25:51,270 --> 00:25:52,030
Is that so?

576
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:54,030
I see you still have

577
00:25:54,030 --> 00:25:56,230
quite a few client complaints piled up.

578
00:25:57,470 --> 00:25:58,670
Well,

579
00:25:59,270 --> 00:26:01,510
those clients

580
00:26:01,530 --> 00:26:02,640
have been pretty difficult lately.

581
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:03,480
So I figured,

582
00:26:03,500 --> 00:26:06,350
if I want to create
the most value for the hotel,

583
00:26:06,350 --> 00:26:09,110
I should be ready
to switch tracks at any time.

584
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,510
Please don't worry, Mr. Ji.

585
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:12,510
I'll smooth things over
with my existing clients.

586
00:26:12,510 --> 00:26:14,350
It won't affect
the new project's operation.

587
00:26:14,350 --> 00:26:16,350
I'd rather you not move so fast.

588
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:18,640
Pick a lane and go deep.

589
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:20,040
Show some results first.

590
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,110
You're right, Mr. Ji.

591
00:26:25,110 --> 00:26:27,240
I'll deal with my client issues first.

592
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:28,270
Organize and wrap up

593
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:30,150
the projects you're currently

594
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:31,310
handling.

595
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:33,750
As for the Lubot project,

596
00:26:33,750 --> 00:26:36,510
let Ms. Xu get some practice on it.

597
00:26:38,110 --> 00:26:38,640
Okay.

598
00:26:39,250 --> 00:26:41,210
If you need me for the new project,

599
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,640
just let me know anytime.

600
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:43,100
Okay.

601
00:26:54,490 --> 00:26:55,110
Mr. Lu,

602
00:26:55,110 --> 00:26:56,110
rest assured.

603
00:26:56,590 --> 00:26:58,520
I will double-check the contract.

604
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:04,310
No trouble at all.

605
00:27:04,310 --> 00:27:06,070
It's our job to verify the details.

606
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:07,830
I'll go over the contract again tonight,

607
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,350
and send the final version to Manager Wu

608
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,840
for confirmation, okay?

609
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:12,550
Alright. See you tomorrow at 9 AM.

610
00:27:12,550 --> 00:27:14,030
Please give me a few more clues.

611
00:27:14,030 --> 00:27:17,030
I've been waiting for
Mr. Zhang for almost a month now.

612
00:27:47,110 --> 00:27:48,160
Ms. Lu?

613
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:52,130
Mr. Duan.

614
00:27:52,830 --> 00:27:53,750
Hello.

615
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:54,740
What's wrong?

616
00:27:55,510 --> 00:27:56,270
My car's

617
00:27:56,590 --> 00:27:58,170
tire is a bit flat,

618
00:27:58,510 --> 00:28:00,590
but I have to meet a client right now.

619
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:01,510
Where to?

620
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,590
Pudong.

621
00:28:02,670 --> 00:28:04,350
Let's go. I'll give you a ride.

622
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:05,330
Thank you.

623
00:28:54,180 --> 00:28:56,330
[Lu Zhenzhen]

624
00:29:01,590 --> 00:29:02,680
Hello, Ms. Lu?

625
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:05,240
Ms. Xu, did you check the group chat?

626
00:29:08,830 --> 00:29:09,830
Here's the thing.

627
00:29:10,350 --> 00:29:11,590
Could you please

628
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:13,390
go to Jiqing Chemical tomorrow?

629
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:24,960
Their boss is coming back tonight

630
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:27,880
and will leave for a business trip
early tomorrow morning.

631
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:29,030
Our department has some documents

632
00:29:29,030 --> 00:29:31,160
that must be handed to him personally.

633
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,160
No one else is available.

634
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:36,920
I have to accompany a client
to the development zone early tomorrow.

635
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:38,780
I can only ask you to make the trip.

636
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:47,120
You have another
contract signing tomorrow?

637
00:29:47,790 --> 00:29:49,990
Can you reschedule it to the afternoon?

638
00:29:51,350 --> 00:29:52,510
I'm sorry.

639
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:54,590
Alright.

640
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:55,590
Great.

641
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:57,920
I'll send you the materials later.

642
00:29:57,920 --> 00:29:59,380
Please review them for me.

643
00:30:00,410 --> 00:30:01,920
Thanks. Appreciate it.

644
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:19,220
[Lu Zhenzhen]
[Jiqing Chemical Conference Layout Draft]

645
00:30:50,910 --> 00:30:52,440
[Sales Office]

646
00:30:52,810 --> 00:30:55,060
[Jiqing Chemical
Conference Activity Process]

647
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:50,440
It really is Mr. Lu's car.

648
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,330
Mr. Duan,

649
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,680
Ms. Lu said

650
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:54,880
that Xu Miyu's already
arrived at Jiqing Chemical.

651
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:57,150
The signing will probably
be this afternoon.

652
00:31:57,150 --> 00:31:58,920
Please make good use of these three hours.

653
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,000
I wish you success.

654
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,990
Three hours is way too long.

655
00:32:02,090 --> 00:32:02,850
Let's go.

656
00:32:04,080 --> 00:32:04,900
[Purong Hotel
Accommodation & Event Service Contract]

657
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:08,560
[Party A: Lubot
Intelligent Storm Technology Co., Ltd.]

658
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:09,190
[Party B: Purong Hotel Co., Ltd.]

659
00:32:09,210 --> 00:32:09,940
[Authorized Representative : Xu Miyu]

660
00:32:10,130 --> 00:32:11,270
What's going on here?

661
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:12,510
You didn't go to Jiqing Chemical?

662
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:13,290
I did.

663
00:32:13,590 --> 00:32:14,640
I delivered the documents.

664
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:16,210
Then when did you sign with Lubot?

665
00:32:16,210 --> 00:32:17,690
Isn't there a date on it?

666
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:24,680
Mr. Duan.

667
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:26,520
Lu Zhenzhen, get over here!

668
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:30,540
Let me explain, Mr. Duan.

669
00:32:45,830 --> 00:32:48,440
Xu Miyu, just you wait.

670
00:32:59,260 --> 00:33:01,880
[Mr. Lu]

671
00:33:04,950 --> 00:33:10,490
[Mr. Lu]

672
00:33:10,830 --> 00:33:11,340
[Mr. Sheng]

673
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:17,830
Hello, Ms. Xu?

674
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,680
Hello?

675
00:33:19,110 --> 00:33:21,070
Mr. Sheng, I'm sorry.

676
00:33:21,070 --> 00:33:22,550
I didn't mean to disturb you so late.

677
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:23,350
Disturb?

678
00:33:23,790 --> 00:33:24,390
Not at all.

679
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:26,160
We're having a dinner party.

680
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:27,840
Come and join us.

681
00:33:28,310 --> 00:33:29,640
No, thank you.

682
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:31,310
I was just wondering

683
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:33,270
if you know where Mr. Lu is.

684
00:33:34,030 --> 00:33:34,830
Wait a moment.

685
00:33:36,270 --> 00:33:36,990
Hello?

686
00:33:37,490 --> 00:33:38,650
H-Hello?

687
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:39,920
Hello?

688
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:41,140
Is this Ms. Xu?

689
00:33:41,170 --> 00:33:42,350
Mr. Lu?

690
00:33:42,370 --> 00:33:43,110
Sorry,

691
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:44,550
I didn't have my phone on me.

692
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:45,830
What's up?

693
00:33:45,830 --> 00:33:46,550
It's fine.

694
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:47,830
I just wanted to tell you

695
00:33:47,830 --> 00:33:51,350
-about tomorrow's signing. I...
-Come and tell me in person.

696
00:33:51,350 --> 00:33:52,920
We're all good friends here.

697
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,110
You must come.

698
00:33:54,130 --> 00:33:55,530
We'll be waiting for you.

699
00:34:00,030 --> 00:34:00,960
Top sales rep,

700
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:02,820
why are you working so late again?

701
00:34:02,830 --> 00:34:04,630
You must not have had dinner yet.

702
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:07,110
I-I'm in a hurry to meet a client.

703
00:34:07,830 --> 00:34:09,510
What client? Where?

704
00:34:09,550 --> 00:34:10,440
I can't talk right now.

705
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:11,590
I really have to go.

706
00:34:11,590 --> 00:34:12,760
I'll report to you tomorrow, okay?

707
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:13,510
Bye.

708
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,600
Tell me before you go.

709
00:34:17,590 --> 00:34:19,360
It's Mr. Lu from Lubot.

710
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:21,300
We were supposed
to sign tomorrow morning,

711
00:34:21,300 --> 00:34:23,400
but something urgent came up for me.

712
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:25,360
And it turns out Mr. Lu's free tonight.

713
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,590
So you're in a hurry to sign?

714
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:27,320
They're having dinner.

715
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,840
I'll see if I have a chance
to get it signed.

716
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:30,000
So you're going

717
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:31,460
to their dinner right now?

718
00:34:32,670 --> 00:34:34,070
Do you know
how many people will be there?

719
00:34:34,070 --> 00:34:34,840
No.

720
00:34:34,860 --> 00:34:35,670
Does anyone else

721
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:37,070
know about this besides me?

722
00:34:37,070 --> 00:34:38,000
No.

723
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:39,730
Do you think you can pull it off?

724
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:41,190
I...

725
00:34:41,510 --> 00:34:42,420
I didn't think that much.

726
00:34:42,420 --> 00:34:44,880
A top sales rep
hits the target with one shot.

727
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:48,320
Let's go.

728
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,110
Where to?

729
00:34:49,510 --> 00:34:51,000
I'll go with you.

730
00:34:56,670 --> 00:34:57,590
Impressive.

731
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:00,250
Truly impressive.

732
00:35:00,510 --> 00:35:03,240
So you came up with this scheme
to turn the tables.

733
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,190
Tell me the truth.

734
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:05,280
That night,

735
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:07,070
did you deliberately
hide at the hotel's back door

736
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:08,150
to be her knight in shining armor?

737
00:35:08,150 --> 00:35:09,360
I went with her

738
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:11,150
to get the deal signed.

739
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:12,190
Got a problem with that?

740
00:35:12,190 --> 00:35:13,190
Not at all.

741
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:15,360
It's brilliant. And handsome too.

742
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:18,840
Come in.

743
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:19,590
Mr. Ji,

744
00:35:19,590 --> 00:35:21,110
the banquet hall is ready.

745
00:35:21,110 --> 00:35:22,670
Ms. Xu is already there.

746
00:35:23,030 --> 00:35:24,630
Okay, we'll be right there.

747
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,510
Thanks for your hard work.

748
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:26,240
It's my duty.

749
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:36,320
Dating really changes a person.

750
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:47,760
Agibot,

751
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:50,580
are you satisfied with
today's pre-launch event?

752
00:35:50,580 --> 00:35:52,670
This event is truly a great success.

753
00:35:52,670 --> 00:35:53,590
I love it.

754
00:35:54,100 --> 00:35:56,210
It's so smart.

755
00:35:56,440 --> 00:36:00,100
But just like good flavor requires
more than just good technique—

756
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:01,590
it needs personality,

757
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:02,590
awareness,

758
00:36:02,590 --> 00:36:03,510
and aesthetics.

759
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:05,100
AI still has a long way to go

760
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:07,060
when it comes to creativity.

761
00:36:07,230 --> 00:36:08,800
Take this little pastry, for example.

762
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:10,440
To truly win over diners,

763
00:36:10,630 --> 00:36:12,320
AI would have to study it for a long time.

764
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,230
Indeed.

765
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,510
The warmth of craftsmanship

766
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:16,320
often requires years of refinement.

767
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:18,670
But AI works nonstop.

768
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:22,410
It can be more efficient and more
precise in improving productivity.

769
00:36:22,410 --> 00:36:24,110
Coming to this launch event today,

770
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:25,320
I'm even more convinced

771
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,070
that nothing

772
00:36:26,070 --> 00:36:28,070
can stop this era from arriving.

773
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,510
A superior and subordinate

774
00:36:32,510 --> 00:36:34,840
who work together so seamlessly like you.

775
00:36:35,630 --> 00:36:36,690
I really envy that.

776
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,320
I mean,

777
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:42,070
that kind of work environment
is the best for cultivating talent.

778
00:36:42,070 --> 00:36:43,070
Ms. Xu is

779
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:44,030
nothing like any other

780
00:36:44,030 --> 00:36:45,330
salesperson I've met.

781
00:36:45,580 --> 00:36:48,190
I often find myself
guessing what she'll do next.

782
00:36:48,190 --> 00:36:49,670
I've been trying to figure her out,

783
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:51,320
only to realize
she has no ulterior motive at all.

784
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:52,580
Did you teach her that?

785
00:36:54,670 --> 00:36:55,880
I get it.

786
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:58,680
Mr. Lu saying is that
I'm not professional enough.

787
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:01,120
It's called being relaxed.

788
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:03,920
Mr. Ji, you should know
what I'm talking about.

789
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:06,440
Our Ms. Xu is indeed

790
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:08,440
different from other salespeople.

791
00:37:08,670 --> 00:37:10,790
She is not the aggressive type.

792
00:37:11,110 --> 00:37:12,710
Kind of like how I feel about Kuanli—

793
00:37:12,710 --> 00:37:14,380
solid but rigid.

794
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:17,080
There's a strange arrogance to it.

795
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:20,230
Large groups have a habit
of choosing the people,

796
00:37:20,230 --> 00:37:21,630
not the other way around.

797
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:23,190
At Purong Hotel,

798
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:25,400
we also strive for high

799
00:37:25,400 --> 00:37:26,530
and high standards.

800
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:28,030
But by "high," we don't mean

801
00:37:28,030 --> 00:37:30,070
being harsh to our employees

802
00:37:30,070 --> 00:37:32,030
or filtering our clients.

803
00:37:32,630 --> 00:37:34,630
Then what kind of "high" do you mean?

804
00:37:35,590 --> 00:37:38,990
It's the kind where your feet lift
half an inch off the ground.

805
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:44,030
W-What do you mean?

806
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:45,600
What I mean is,

807
00:37:45,630 --> 00:37:48,150
we want every guest
who walks into Purong Hotel

808
00:37:48,150 --> 00:37:49,320
to feel that little lift—

809
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:51,980
the joy of being
half an inch off the ground.

810
00:37:52,070 --> 00:37:55,070
It's not a life-changing feeling,

811
00:37:55,070 --> 00:37:55,710
but rather a way

812
00:37:55,710 --> 00:37:58,280
for people to temporarily detach

813
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,630
from real life,

814
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:00,960
and then discover that

815
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:03,090
there is a life worth longing for here.

816
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:04,840
A like worth longing for.

817
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,160
That's my slogan too.

818
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:08,120
It knows again.

819
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:09,880
After going around in circles,

820
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:12,540
it turns out we want the same thing.

821
00:38:13,590 --> 00:38:15,030
Even though

822
00:38:15,030 --> 00:38:16,710
tech research and service seem to be

823
00:38:16,710 --> 00:38:18,150
two unrelated industries,

824
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:21,030
what we do is actually similar.

825
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:22,880
We're both dedicated to

826
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:25,480
making small improvements
in people's lives.

827
00:38:25,710 --> 00:38:26,670
Well said.

828
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:27,510
Our Lubot

829
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:29,960
is fairly successful

830
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:31,590
in China's AI industry,

831
00:38:31,590 --> 00:38:32,110
but

832
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:35,030
compared to tycoons in other industries,

833
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:36,600
we're still small in scale

834
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:38,290
and limited in budget.

835
00:38:39,230 --> 00:38:40,880
I understand that different industries

836
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:43,030
have vastly different business models

837
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:44,510
and consumer habits.

838
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:45,230
We will absolutely not use

839
00:38:45,230 --> 00:38:46,510
service standards from other industries

840
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:49,310
to presume your company's
concerns and troubles.

841
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:51,200
You can rest assured about that.

842
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:52,710
Good.

843
00:38:52,710 --> 00:38:54,230
I'll have my assistant

844
00:38:54,230 --> 00:38:56,110
send over our company's
specific requirements later.

845
00:38:56,110 --> 00:38:57,670
Then we'll schedule

846
00:38:57,670 --> 00:39:00,230
a meeting with representatives
from the other departments.

847
00:39:00,230 --> 00:39:02,400
Okay. Thank you for your trust, Mr. Lu.

848
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:05,110
I won't let you down.

849
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:06,590
Glad to work with you.

850
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:07,190
